&gt; There is a growl from Tucson, followed by a ground shaking roar.  He too had
&gt; suffered many injustices from the Predacons, yet he tries to put that behind
&gt; him as he sees the need to put the past behind him and move ahead.  The
&gt; future depended on it.  In his draconic form he leaps in front of Rodimus,
&gt; staring him in the eyes.
&gt;
&gt; &quot;  No, it may look as if I am but in truth I am trying to make a point!  Yes
&gt; we have both lost a great deal to our enemy but we will lose something.
&gt; GREATER if we don&#39;t learn to. PUT THE PAST BEHIND US!  TIL ALL ARE ONE, were
&gt; the words of Primus. Till all are one.  Unicron is far beyond our factions
&gt; alone but, if we work as one faction we have a chance to overpower this new
&gt; threat.  That is what I am trying to convey.  Leo Prime, that also applies
&gt; to you, you may not understand my reasoning but in time you will.&quot;

&lt;NEW&gt;

RODIMUS PRIME just looked at TUSCON as if he has just lost his mind,
his optics still smoldering with his own inner emotions. &quot;You started
this mission in an effort to wipe out the evil.&quot; He said in clipped
tones. &quot;And yet here we are trying to work with them to destroy a
greater evil.&quot;

He turned to look at TUSCON, optic to optic. &quot;And what do you think
they will do should they gain the upper hand, or when this is over?&quot;

Folded his arms across his chest he just looked at TUSCON. &quot;Now is not
the time for discussions like this. But if you think I will work with
Cyclonus or any other Predacon without my hand on my weapon and my
guard up, then you don&#39;t know me.&quot;

 &quot;I will finish this mission as is needed.&quot; RODIMUS PRIME said as he
stepped around TUSCON to continue towards the Dinosaurs. &quot;Then me and
you are going to talk.&quot;

